Dialogue. Invitation for the dinner.

A: Good evening Mr. Fischer. Glad to see you at this meetup! Thank you for such AN interesting lecture! Let me invite you for a cup of tea?

B: Oh, Artem. What a wonderful meeting! Of course, my dear friend! Do you know a good place nearby?

A: There is a very nice and cosy cafe just rigt the corner!

B: Thank you for invitation! I`d love to come! But I want to listen TO a presentation from Mr. Giovanny! Can we meet at 18.00?

A: Shure! I`m looking forward to it!

B: Me too! So see you at 18.00 at that cafe!